        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"246273\">@Bhavik Mehta</span>, do you think you could put together a TODO list of the facts we need? What new design do we need? We still don't have anthing about filtered colimits, or finitary monads. I guess we would need to decide which of \"Lawvere theory / equational theory / any appropriately finite universal algebra thing\" is appropriate.</p>",
